prompts.frontCover: A charming and humorous cartoon watercolor scene. A slightly bewildered, fluffy gray cat is sitting in a lopsided, hand-built cardboard box rocket ship. The rocket has "AGE IS IRRELEVANT" clumsily scrawled on the side with a crayon. The cat wears a tiny, askew party hat. Floating around the rocket are whimsical, pastel-colored planets and stars. In the center, below the cat, the greeting "happy birthday" is written in a beautiful, flowing, and readable handwritten cursive script. The entire illustration is rendered in a soft, lighthearted watercolor style, featuring visible brush strokes, delicate color bleeds, and a subtle paper texture, creating a funny and endearing flat 2D artwork.
